}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4182698635109247", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8425157384196663"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1724129697, "id": "8413493978696337", "version": "2.3.23", "version_code": 53, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8413491928696542"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4182698635109247", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8425157384196663"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1108251989650391"}]}, "change_log": "Enhancements:\n\n\ud83d\udc64  Single Player / Practice - Five New Female AI Opponents, hailing from Colombia, Japan, Canada, Czechia, and Great Britain.\n- 1 Female AI player available for free to play players\n- All AI players available with Match Point Tennis Pro\n\n\ud83d\udd0a Audio - AI Opponents now grunt when making challenging shots or difficult returns. Control the volume of the grunts under SETTINGS > AUDIO > AI Audio\n\n\ud83c\udf89 Center Marker - See an X on the floor to mark your center position. Reset your center by pressing and holding the Meta/Oculus button for 3 seconds while in game.\n\n\u23f0  Serve Clock - A 25 second serve clock has been added to multiplayer.\n\n\ud83c\udfc3 Movement Alignment - Two new movement alignment options:\n- Headset-Based Movement: Play is aligned to your headset. Use this option if you have limited space or you typically 